    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This driver-focused example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term mechanical integrity, the rod bearings have been replaced and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to mitigate floor-pan fatigue. The suspension geometry remains precise with recently refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior and interior exhibit a minor patina consistent with spirited use, the chassis remains stiff and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This is a mechanically sorted performance machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
