    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. This car has been a dependable companion, kept primarily in a covered garage and serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though closer inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway driving. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and well-preserved; the leather seating is supple with no rips or thinning, and the dashboard remains crack-free. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, are in full working order. Mechanically, the car is robust\u2014the engine idles smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Within the last 5,000 miles, we have replaced the brake pads, performed a professional alignment, and installed a fresh set of all-season tires. This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality car without the new-car price tag. Full service records are organized and ready for your review.",
      "price": 34500.0,
